            <lg xml:id="TK857">
<l>mikaṉmēvu meypporuḷ kāṇā rikalmēvu </l>
<l>miṉṉā vaṟivi ṉavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those whose judgement brings misery through its connection with hatred cannot understand the triumphant nature of truth.</l>
